            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(SN) In nomine domini Dei eterni. Anno dominice incarnacionis millesimo C
                        XXX sexto, XII die intrante mensis iunii, indicione XIIII. Constat nos
                            <persName
                            key="#marriage #Roman #childOf #Witness #Venditio #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                                ><name ref="Gausus/de Pillanicha">Gaitho</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs>
                        <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Azo/de Pillanicha"
                            >Azoni</name></persName> de loco <placeName key="#Villas" ref="#places/4146"
                            >Pillanicha</placeName> et <persName
                            key="#marriage #Roman #Witness #Venditio #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                                ><name ref="Patavina">Patavina</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">iugalibus</rs>, qui professi sumus lege vivere <rs
                            key="#Roman">Romana</rs>, ipso namque iugale meo mihi consenciente et
                        subter confirmante, in presentia <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs> accepimus
                        nos a te <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Missus #Priors #Monks #Venditio #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2075">Sancti Cipriani</orgName>, per <rs
                            key="#Missus">nucium</rs> tuum <persName key="#Missus #Priors"
                            ref="#people/3550">Retholfum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">priorem</rs>, qui est constructus in <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/914">Venecia</placeName>, in loco qui
                        dicitur <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/4147">Murane</placeName>,
                            <rs key="#Price">argenti denariorum bonorum de Verone libras C et
                            quinquaginta</rs>, finitum precium sicut inter nobis convenit pro totam
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> nostraa quam nos abemus et
                        tenemus a <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietate</rs>, sive per
                        hereditatem sive per <rs key="#Venditio">cartulas vendicionis</rs>, iuris
                        nostris que nos abere et posidere visi summus per nos et per rusticis
                        nostris in <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/125"><rs
                                key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/13"
                            >Tervisiano</placeName></geogName> et in eius terretorio, et iacet
                        iamscripta terra in <rs key="#Villas">villa</rs> Pilanicha et in eius
                        finibus, et in villa <placeName key="#Villas" ref="#places/4433">Caltana</placeName> et in eius
                        finibus, ut dictum est, iamscripta terra, tam <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs>
                        cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">sediminibus</rs> seu <rs key="#Cereals"
                            >terris arabilis</rs>, vigris, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs> cum areis
                        suarum, <rs key="#Cereals #Legumes">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder #Animals">pascuis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs> ac stallareis, <rs key="#Shores">ripis</rs>,
                        rupinis, <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venationibus, capulo,
                            pasculo</rs>, cultis et incultis, divisis et indivisis, una cum finibus,
                        terminibus, accessionibus et usibus aquarum, quarumque ductibus, cum omni
                        iure ac iacenciis et pertinenciis a infrascripta terra pertinentibus in
                        integrum. Que autem infrascripta terra iuris nostri superius dicta, una cum
                        accessionibus et ingressibus seu cum superioribus et inferioribus eorum,
                        qualiter superius legitur, in integrum ab hac die tibi cui supra monasterio
                        Sancti Cipriani pro infrascripto precio vendimus, tradimus, emancipamus,
                        nulli alii vendita, donata, alienata, obnoxiata vel tradita nisi tibi,
                        faciendum exinde a presenti die tu et <rs key="#Monks">monachis</rs> et
                        ordinariis tuis iuste et legaliter quicquid volueritis, sine omni nostra et
                        heredum nostrorum contradicionem. Quidem espondimus atque promittimus nos
                        qul supra Gaitho et Patavina iugalibus, una cum nostris heredibus tibi cui
                        supra monasterio tuisque monachis qui pro tempore ibidem ordinati fuerint,
                        aut cui vos secundum legem dederitis iamscriptam vendicionem qualiter
                        superius legitur in integrum ab omni homine defensare; quam si defendere non
                        potuerimus aut si vobis exinde aliquid quovis ingenium subtrahere
                        quesierimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> eandem vendicionem ut
                        supra legitur vobis restituamus sicut pro tempore fuerit meliorata aut
                        valuerit, sub estimacione in consimili terra cum edificiis supra in
                        consimilibus locis. Et nec nobis liceat ullo tempore nolle quod voluimus et
                        quod a nobis semel factum vel conscriptum est sub iure iurando
                        inviolabiliter conservare promittimus cum stipulacione subnixa. Actum in
                        villa Pillanicha. Feliciter. Signum +++++ manibus iamscriptis Gaitho et
                        Patavina iugalibus, qui hanc cartulam vendicionis fieri rogaverunt ut supra.
                        Signum +++++ manuum <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Aicardus/de Spinitha">Aicardus</name></persName> de Spinitha,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Venditio #siblingOf #childOf"><name
                                ref="Patavinus">Patavinus</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio #siblingOf #childOf"><name ref="Rodulfus"
                                >Rothulfo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">germani</rs> filios <persName key="#parentOf"><name
                                ref="Dominicus/de Gumpo">Dominici</name> de Gumpo</persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Iohannes/de Ugo"
                                >Iohannes</name> de Ugo</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Hubertus/de Mesenda">Ubertus</name>
                            de Mesenda</persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Rainerius/de Mora">Rainero</name> de Mora</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Iohannes/de Blanco">Iohannes</name>
                            de Blanco</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio #Specialized_workers"><name
                                ref="Daibertus/faber">Daibertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Specialized_workers">faber</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Petrus/de Athrine">Petrus</name> de
                            Athrine</persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Ermannus/de Azo">Ermanno</name> de Azo</persName>. (SN ) Ego
                            <persName key="#Notary #Writer #Venditio"><name ref="Florentius"
                                >Florencius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>
                        <rs key="#Writer">scriptor</rs> huius cartule vendicionis post tradita
                        conplevi. </ab>
                </div>
